name: 6uild 6ack 6etter
description:
Conspiracy theory Collection 
First Song in Collection

“Build back better“ is a term used by politicians around the world. In a positive way it seems like a good word. But if you change the “b” to “6”, you will get the number 6 in front of 3 digits, like a pledge that you are a member of the illuminate.
